const dataReducer=(state=initialState,action) => {

    switch(action.type) {
        case "UPDATE_USER_TYPE": return {...state,authenticationData: action.payload}
        case "UPDATE_ALL_EVENTS": return {...state,allEvents: action.payload}
        case "ALL_FLOW_TIME": return {...state,airflowTime: action.payload}
        case "ALL_WEBSITE": return {...state,allWebsite: action.payload}
        case "ADHOC_RUN_RES_DATA": return {...state,AdhocRunResponse: action.payload}
        case "ADHOC_RUN_SHOW_RESULT": return {...state,showAdhocRunResult: action.payload}

        case "UPDATE_SELECTED_TENANT": return {...state,selectedTenant: action.payload}
        case "UPDATE_ALL_TABLES": return {...state,allTables: action.payload}
        case "UPDATE_COMPUTED_EVENTS": return {...state,computedEvents: action.payload}
        case "UPDATE_TRANSACTIONAL_EVENTS": return {...state,transactionalEvents: action.payload}

        case "UPDATE_BEHAVIORAL_EVENTS": return {...state,behavioralEvents: action.payload}
        case "UPDATE_SELECTED_EVENT": return {...state,selectedEvent: action.payload}
        case "UPDATE_ACTIVE_TAB": return {...state,activeTab: action.payload}


        case "UPDATE_SELECTED_EVENT_META": return {...state,selectedEventMeta: action.payload}
        case "UPDATE_SELECTED_FIELDS": return {...state,selectedFields: action.payload}
        case "UPDATE_HIGHLIGHTED_EVENT": return {...state,highlightedEvent: action.payload}
        case "UPDATE_DB_LIST": return {...state,dbList: action.payload}
        case "UPDATE_STALE_COMPUTED_EVENTS": return {...state,staleComputedEvents: action.payload}
        case "UPDATE_STALE_TRANSACTIONAL_EVENTS": return {...state,staleTransactionalEvents: action.payload}
        case "UPDATE_STALE_BEHAVIORAL_EVENTS": return {...state,staleBehavioralEvents: action.payload}
        case "UPDATE_FRESH_COMPUTED_EVENTS": return {...state,freshComputedEvents: action.payload}
        case "UPDATE_FRESH_TRANSACTIONAL_EVENTS": return {...state,freshTransactionalEvents: action.payload}
        case "UPDATE_FRESH_BEHAVIORAL_EVENTS": return {...state,freshBehavioralEvents: action.payload}
        case "UPDATE_PROCESSED_RECORDS": return {...state,processedRecords: action.payload}
        case "UPDATE_PROCESSED_RECORDS_COUNT": return {...state,processedRecordsCount: action.payload}
        case "UPDATE_PERSISTANCE_RECORDS": return {...state,persistanceTimeRecord: action.payload}



        case "UPDATE_SQOOP_DATA_COUNT": return {...state,sqoopCount: action.payload}
        case "UPDATE_MAXWELL_DATA_COUNT": return {...state,maxwellCount: action.payload}
        case "UPDATE_MONGO_DATA_COUNT": return {...state,mongoCount: action.payload}



        default: return state;
    }
}

export default dataReducer
